    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the difference between Canva AI, Adobe Firefly, and Recraft?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Canva AI is an all-in-one design platform with AI features baked into a template ecosystem, ideal for social media and marketing content. Adobe Firefly is a generative AI engine integrated into Creative Cloud, best for professionals who need commercial-grade AI generation. Recraft specializes in vector graphics (SVG output) and brand-consistent design systems."
      }
