        "text": "Adobe Firefly offers free generations up to a daily limit with watermarked outputs. Full access requires a Creative Cloud subscription starting at $59.99/month or a Firefly-specific plan. Canva AI has a generous free tier, while Recraft offers a free plan with limited monthly credits."
