      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, all three tools offer commercial usage rights on paid plans. Canva AI includes commercial use with Pro plans ($13/month). Adobe Firefly is legally trained and commercially safe for marketing and content creation. Recraft's paid plans include commercial licensing. Always review the specific terms for your use case."
      }
    }
