<tr><td><strong>Ease of Use</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Best in class</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐ Good (with CC experience)</td><td>⭐⭐⭐ Moderate learning curve</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>AI Image Gen</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐ Solid</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Stunning</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐ Good, vector-focused</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Vector / SVG Output</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐ Basic shapes only</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐ Illustrator vectors</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Native SVG</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Brand Consistency</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐ Brand Kit</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐ CC Libraries</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Style training + kits</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Template Library</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Massive</td><td>⭐⭐⭐ Limited (Express)</td><td>⭐⭐⭐ Niche templates</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Commercial Safety</strong></td><td>✅ Yes</td><td>✅ Yes (best in class)</td><td>✅ Yes</td></tr>
